  <p>
    Tutor4u provides a platform that connects students with highly qualified tutors in a wide variety of subjects.</p>
  <p>
    In order to connect with tutors, please follow the following steps:</p>
  <ol>
    <li> Sign up as a tutee and set up your tutee profile.</li>
    <li> Press the "Request a Tutor" button on our front page and write down the subjects you want to get tutored in.</li>
    <li> Write down the time during which you are available. </li>
    <li> Browse the list of available tutors and contact them to set up a location for tutoring. </li></ol>
  
  <p> In order to become a tutor, please follow the following steps:</p>
  <ol>
    <li> Sign up as a tutor and set up your tutor profile with appropriate contact information.</li>
    <li> Write down the subjects you can tutor in.</li>
    <li> Record the grades in the subjects you want to tutor in. </li>
    <li> Write down the times during which you are free to tutor a student</li>
  </ol>
